relation: Eco-Cuisine Betty Brownie Mix with Vanilla
Eco-Cuisine Ground Beef Style Quick Mix
1 lb. bag/10 bags per box or 25 lb. bulk box
textBeforeTable: The baking mix products were distributed nationwide through direct sales and food service distribution centers. Products affected are: The Missouri Department of Health and Senior Services received information regarding a recall of Eco-Cuisine baking mix products because it has the potential to be contaminated with Salmonella. Healthy persons infected with Salmonella often experience fever, diarrhea (which may be bloody), nausea, vomiting and abdominal pain.
